{"type":"message","id":"c338a22f","parentId":"3e7cd510","timestamp":"2026-03-25T02:03:39.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No pude comprobarlo desde aquí porque esa validación pide aprobación de ejecución y por WhatsApp no se puede aprobar ese comando.\n\nSi quieres, apruébalo desde la Web UI / terminal y corro exactamente esto:\n\n```powershell\n$headers = @{ Authorization = \"Bearer $env:NOTION_TOKEN\"; \"Notion-Version\" = \"2022-06-28\" }\nif (-not $env:NOTION_TOKEN) { Write-Output \"NOTION_TOKEN_MISSING\"; exit 0 }\ntry {\n  $resp = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri \"https://api.notion.com/v1/users/me\" -Headers $headers\n  $name = if ($resp.name) { $resp.name } elseif ($resp.bot.name) { $resp.bot.name } else { \"(sin nombre)\" }\n  Write-Output (\"NOTION_OK|name=\" + $name + \"|type=\" + $resp.type)\n} catch {\n  Write-Output (\"NOTION_ERR|\" + $_.Exception.Message)\n}\n```\n\nO te doy una verificación manual rápida para que la pegues tú mismo en PowerShell.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_030d1769d3806aff0169c3427a70fc819194fb752bea73b3f5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":214,"output":239,"cacheRead":16640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17093,"cost":{"input":0.000535,"output":0.003585,"cacheRead":0.00416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00828}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774404209898,"responseId":"resp_030d1769d3806aff0169c34275f0a8819195a6a9258ce60e4e"}}
