{"type":"message","id":"2b6ba9f6","parentId":"76e8346a","timestamp":"2026-03-25T02:04:41.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfecto. `ffmpeg` está instalado y operativo en esta máquina.\n\nPuntos útiles:\n- versión: `8.1-full_build-www.gyan.dev`\n- incluye `libwhisper`\n- trae soporte amplio de codecs y aceleración (`nvenc`, `nvdec`, `d3d11va`, `vulkan`, etc.)\n\nSi quieres, el siguiente paso es verificar si también está `ffprobe`, o ya usarlo para alguna tarea concreta.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_030d1769d3806aff0169c342bb69a48191a08dcc3331cbfe30\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":13426,"output":103,"cacheRead":4608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18137,"cost":{"input":0.033565000000000005,"output":0.001545,"cacheRead":0.001152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.036262}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774404278021,"responseId":"resp_030d1769d3806aff0169c342b9f51c8191aa32b87d51f6265d"}}
